'''Kalarba Safari''' was a company owned by [[Jarth Pitareeze|Jarth]] and [[Meg Pitareeze]] that provided touring services to the [[Ancestral Lands of Kalarba]]. The tour, known as "[[Journey of the Spirit]]," took place aboard the ''[[Tharen Wayfarer]]'', taking visitors to [[Kalarba/Legends|Kalarba]] past the [[Great Sea (Kalarba)|Great Sea]] and [[Three Peaks of Tharen]]. While on the voyage, [[Droid/Legends|droids]] [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] catered to guests' needs and provided food such as [[Stenness pie]].

